nodes.text: The Trade Federation fleet, or simply referred to as the Federation fleet, was the merchant fleet of the Trade Federation and naval branch of the Federation military. When the Federation joined the Confederacy of Independent Systems, its fleet joined the Separatist navy.

The Trade Federation fleet first appeared in Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace, which was first released on May 19, 1999, and was first identified in the 2015 reference book Ultimate Star Wars published by Dorling Kindersley.
